<T>__{dissolve to:}
<L>__{exterior montana plain dusk (in flashback)}
<A>__{moving angle, rushing with dizzy swiftness over the prairie, over waving grasses... a long passage... before we come at last to the girl clarice, sitting with her lamb, hunched in despair. she rises, her face tear stained, and turns from us. holding the lamb, she starts back the way she came...}
<T>__{cut to:}
<L>__{exterior country dirt road night bright moonlight}
<A>__{moving angle, very rapid, down this road... coming at last to a stopped highway patrol car. clarice, with her lamb, is standing in the car's headlights. she starts wearily towards the sheriff...}
